<item>
  <title>New Research Shows a Troubling Trend for Chesapeake Bay Osprey</title>
  <link>https://www.usgs.gov/centers/eesc/news/new-research-shows-a-troubling-trend-chesapeake-bay-osprey?utm_source=comms&amp;amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;amp;utm_campaign=news</link>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>USGS research shows that Osprey reproduction declined when nests were located in areas with higher‑salinity water, a trend observed across multiple areas of the Chesapeake Bay.</p>]]></description>
  <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 12:53:45 EDT</pubDate>
