<item>
  <title>Photo &amp; Video Chronology — Kīlauea summit eruption episode 49</title>
  <link>https://www.usgs.gov/observatories/hvo/news/photo-video-chronology-kilauea-summit-eruption-episode-49?utm_source=comms&amp;amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;amp;utm_campaign=news</link>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Episode 49 of lava fountaining during the ongoing Halemaʻumaʻu eruption at the summit of Kīlauea took place for 7.5 hours on June 14. The eruption is currently paused.<br>&nbsp;</p>]]></description>
  <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 21:52:49 EDT</pubDate>
